<HEADLINE>
AUTO DESIGN: A CADILLAC DESIGN HEADS TOWARD THE EDGE 
</HEADLINE>
   (duplication warning: also sent with `a' code)  
 (bl)  
 By MICHELLE KREBS   
 c.1998 N.Y. Times News Service    
<TEXT>
<P>
