   STUDIO54-OWNER _ NEW YORK _ The boyish grin and the chiseled
good looks from the days when he was co-owner of Studio 54 are
still there. Ian Schrager goes from 0 to 60 in 4 seconds in
describing his plans for a new ``boutique'' line of hotels. And
about the old days at Studio 54. (Blackerby, Palm Beach Post)
