<P>
   HAZING-INITIATIONS (Undated) Hazing is not new to the sports
world, but reports out of New Orleans regarding the incident
involving Saints rookie tight end Cam Cleeland (a former Husky) are
hard to believe. Running through a line of players with a
pillowcase over your head and being beaten with rolled coins in a
bag? A look at the ritual of hazing.
</P>
