<P>
   CLINTON-LEWIS _ OAK BLUFF, Mass. _ President Clinton joins Rep.
John Lewis, D-Ga., in a 2 p.m. EDT event to commemorate the 35th
anniversary of Martin Luther King Jr.'s ''I Have A Dream Speech''
at the March on Washington. (Carr, Cox News Service).
