<P>
   &QL;  PA Contract Awards States News Service Washington, August 28
-- American Environmental Services Inc. of Allison Park won a
$163,750 contract from the Defense Reutilication and Marketing
Service in Battle Creek, Mich., for natural resources and
consveration services.
</P>
