scholarly sideline back in 1982 when he was invited to speak on a
panel on climate and history. ``Just tell them about
air-conditioning,'' his wife, a seventh-generation Floridian,
suggested facetiously. And so began Arsenault's great
air-conditioning adventure. By Janny Scott.
