</P>
<P>
   &UR; (Translated from the Russian by Pavel Palazchenko.) &LR;
</P>
<P>
   &UR; c.1998 LaStampa &LR;  &QC;
</P>
<P>
   &UR; (Mikhail Gorbachev, the last leader of the Soviet Union before
