to New York City's efforts to curtail the pornography industry,
ruling that Show World, a midtown Manhattan porn emporium, and two
other adult video stores can stay in business as long as no more
than 40 percent of their floor space and inventory are dedicated to
adult entertainment. By David Rohde.
</P>
<P>
   CONGO-ARMY-VOLUNTEERS (Kinshasa, Congo) _ Kinshasa is filled
these days with young men who have volunteered to join the army,
compelled by vague notions of duty and the unshakable belief that
Congo has been attacked by the hated Tutsi and their Rwandan
backers. Each morning, except on Sundays, they can be seen milling
around La Cite's sports stadiums, waiting to join the military or
to begin their drills. By Norimitsu Onishi.
</P>
