<P>
   SOC-REVOLUTION (Foxborough, Mass.) _ By Frank Dell'Apa.
</P>
<P>
   CAR-NHIS (Loudon, N.H.) _ By Michael Vega.
</P>
<P>
   BBO-RYAN-COLUMN (Undated) -- It is, I suspect, much more of an
American character trait to care about personal records of any kind
than it is elsewhere. By Bob Ryan.
</P>
