<P>
   CLINTON-TRIP _ WASHINGTON _ An advancer on President Clinton's
first foreign trip since the latest major flap in Monica Lewinsky
scandcal. He will go to Russia and Ireland-Northern Ireland at a
time when both countries could use a major shot in the arm from the
United States -- one, economically, the other, politically. Both
are looking for one thing: stability. But what does it mean for the
United States? And what does it mean for Bill Clinton? (Deans, Cox
News Service).
</P>
<P>
   With/ TRIP-BOX _ WASHINGTON _ A box on specifics of the Clinton
trip. (Deans, Cox News Service).
