   &UR; RUSSIAN UNCERTAINTY AND MARKET TURMOIL &LR;
</P>
<P>
   The New York Times plans an extensive package of stories
relating to both the political and economic turmoil and Russia and
to the related economic turmoil around the world.
</P>
<P>
   These Russia stories are being edited by The Times'  &UR; Foreign
Desk &LR; :
</P>
