<P>
   RUSSIA-RDP (Moscow) _ Developments in Russia: A tired President
Yeltsin bluntly dismissed rumors on Friday that he would quit over
Russia's financial crisis and vowed to serve out his full term to
2000 and then retire; efforts to calm the political and economic
frenzy. By Michael Wines.
</P>
<P>
   These stories will move by  &UR; 8 p.m. Eastern time: &LR;
