govern, it was not much of a success. By Celestine Bohlen.
</P>
<P>
   RUSSIA-EUROPE (Paris) _ The finance ministers of four
economically powerful Western European countries warned Moscow on
Friday that the only way out of its current crisis is to make the
tough economic changes long urged by the International Monetary
Fund. By Craig R. Whitney.
</P>
