   RUSSIA-FUND (Undated) _ The International Monetary Fund has
apparently decided to renegotiate its loan agreement with Russia,
delaying the process until the end of September, if necessary, to
give the Russians time to put a new government firmly in place. By
Louis Uchitelle.
</P>
