 Friday, Aug. 28, 1998     
 Editors     
<TEXT>
<P>
   The Hearst News Service has filed or will file these stories for
Saturday, Sunday and Monday. If you have questions, please call
Susie McBee or Tim Spence at 202-298-6920. For questions about
Houston Chronicle sports stories, please call the Houston Chronicle
Sports Department, 713-220-7896.
</P>
<P>
   &LR;  &QL;
