<SLUG> BC-GRAPHICS-FILES-NYT </SLUG>
  
<TEXT>
<P>
   Here is a listing of the New York Times News Service Macintosh
graphics files that moved Friday, 08/28/98. Included is the
corresponding story slug and the size. All graphics have been
posted on PressLink, NewsCom and the Wieck Photo Database.
</P>
<P>
   CLINTON/Opinions by race -- 2x4 1/2 -- CLINTON-RIGHTS
</P>
<P>
   CONGO/Inga Dam, locator -- 1x2 3/4 -- CONGO-VOLUNTEER
</P>
<P>
   FBC/Bowl matchups equation -- 46px4 1/8 -- FBC-PREVIEW-OVERVIEW
</P>
<P>
   SPEND/Insurance savings -- 2x10 -- SPEND-AUTO-INSURE
</P>
<P>
   WORLD/Dow Days -- 78px4 -- INVEST-WORLD-BEAR-MARKET
</P>
<P>
   INVEST/Airline stocks 8/29 -- 57px2 1/4 -- INVEST-AIRLINES
</P>
<P>
   MUTFUND/401(k) transfer activity -- 1x4 1/4 --
MUTFUND-401-SWITCH
</P>
